OpenAlex HTTP 400 for https://api.openalex.org/works?search=++%23+Flow+of+Thought++Given+supervised+pairs+%24%28x%2Cy%29%24+where+%24y%24+is+%2A%2Afinal+answer+only%2A%2A+%28no+chain-of-thought%29%2C+we+can+learn+a+%2A%2Aprompt-conditioned+latent+ODE%2A%2A+%24%5Cfrac%7Bdz%7D%7Bdt%7D%3Dv_%5Ctheta%28z%2Ct%2Cc%29%24+that+transports+a+simple+prior+%24z%280%29%5Csim%5Cmathcal+N%280%2CI%29%24+to+an+%2A%2Aanswer-conditioned+latent+endpoint%2A%2A+%24z%5E%5Cstar%3D%5Cphi%28y%2Cc%29%24%2C+such+that+decoding+from+%24z%281%29%24+yields+correct+answers+at+competitive+accuracy+%2A%2Awithout+emitting+CoT%2A%2A.++By+applying+%2A%2Arectified+flow+%2F+reflow%2A%2A+to+the+learned+latent+dynamics%2C+we+can+%E2%80%9Cstraighten%E2%80%9D+trajectories+so+that+%2A%2A1%E2%80%934+solver+steps%2A%2A+suffice+at+inference+time%2C+producing+a+tunable+%2A%2Acompute-quality+frontier%2A%2A+%28accuracy+vs.+steps%2Flatency%29+rather+than+a+fixed-cost+reasoning+procedure.+Rectified+flow+is+specifically+motivated+by+the+high+cost+of+ODE%2FSDE-based+sampling+in+diffusion-style+models.+++With+conditional+flow+matching+from+%24z_0%5Csim%5Cmathcal+N%280%2CI%29%24+to+%24z%5E%5Cstar%3D%5Cphi%28y%2Cc%29%24%2C+plus+%2A%2Arectified+reflow+distillation%2A%2A+to+enable+1%E2%80%934-step+inference.+Uses+CoT-free+supervision+%28answer+only%29.++---++%23%23+Method+specification++%23%23%23+Notation+%26+setup++%2A+Dataset+%24%5Cmathcal+D%3D%5C%7B%28x_i%2Cy_i%29%5C%7D%24+where+%24y%24+is+the+%2A%2Afinal+answer+string%2A%2A+%28no+rationales%29.+%2A+Prompt+encoder+%24c%3D%5Cmathrm%7BEnc%7D_%5Comega%28x%29%24+%28could+be+a+frozen+LM+trunk+or+trainable+encoder%29.+%2A+Answer-latent+encoder+%24z%5E%5Cstar%3D%5Cphi_%5Ceta%28y%2Cc%29%5Cin%5Cmathbb+R%5E%7Bd_z%7D%24.+%2A+Latent+dynamics%3A+%24%5Cfrac%7Bdz%7D%7Bdt%7D%3Dv_%5Ctheta%28z%2Ct%2Cc%29%24%2C+%24t%5Cin%5B0%2C1%5D%24%2C+%24z%280%29%3Dz_0%5Csim%5Cmathcal+N%280%2CI%29%24.+%2A+Decoder+%24p_%5Cpsi%28y%5Cmid+x%2C+z%281%29%29%24+that+emits+%2A%2Aanswer+only%2A%2A.++%23%23%23+Endpoint+construction+%24z%5E%5Cstar%3D%5Cphi_%5Ceta%28y%2Cc%29%24+%28crucial%29++You+want+an+endpoint+that%3A++1.+contains+answer+semantics%2C+2%29+is+stable+across+paraphrases%2C+3%29+doesn%E2%80%99t+leak+CoT.++Concrete+choice%3A++%2A+Use+a+frozen+pretrained+LM+%24%28F%29%24.+Run+%24%28F%29%24+on+the+concatenation+%24%5Bx+%5Cmid+%5Ctexttt%7B%3CANS%3E%7D+%5Cmid+y%5D%24.+%2A+Let+%24h_%7B%5Ctext%7Beos%7D%7D%24+be+the+final-layer+hidden+state+at+the+EOS+token+%28or+pooled+answer-token+hidden+states%29.+%2A+Set+%24z%5E%5Cstar+%3D+W+h_%7B%5Ctext%7Beos%7D%7D%24+with+a+learned+projection+%24W%5Cin%5Cmathbb+R%5E%7Bd_z%5Ctimes+d_h%7D%24.+++This+makes+%24z%5E%5Cstar%24+a+%2A%2Arepresentation+of+the+correct+answer+given+the+prompt%2A%2A%2C+without+needing+intermediate+rationales.++%23%23%23+Training+objectives++%23%23%23%23+%28i%29+Conditional+Flow+Matching+loss+%28endpoint-only+%E2%80%9Cteacher%E2%80%9D+path%29++Use+the+simplest+linear+coupling+path+%28mirrors+CFM-style+linear+interpolation+objectives%29.+In+Flow+Matching%2C+CFM+yields+objectives+of+the+form+in+Eq.+%2823%29+for+an+interpolation+%24%5Cpsi_t%24.+++For+our+latent+endpoints%3A++%2A+Sample+%24t%5Csim+%5Cmathcal+U%5B0%2C1%5D%24%2C+%24z_0%5Csim%5Cmathcal+N%280%2CI%29%24+%2A+Define+interpolation%3A+%24z_t%3D%281-t%29z_0%2Bt+z%5E%5Cstar%24+%2A+Target+velocity%3A+%24u+%3D+z%5E%5Cstar+-+z_0%24+%2A+Loss%3A++%24%24%5Cmathcal+L_%7B%5Ctext%7BCFM%7D%7D%28%5Ctheta%29%3D%5Cmathbb+E_%7B%28x%2Cy%29%2Cz_0%2Ct%7D%5Cleft%5B%7Cv_%5Ctheta%28z_t%2Ct%2Cc%29-u%7C_2%5E2%5Cright%5D%24%24++This+is+the+digressing+a+vector+field+along+an+interpolation+path%2C+consistent+with+Flow+Matching-style+regression+objectives.+++%23%23%23%23+%28ii%29+Answer+decoding+loss+%28forces+correctness%2C+discourages+degenerate+endpoints%29++%24%24%5Cmathcal+L_%7B%5Ctext%7Bdec%7D%7D%28%5Cpsi%29%3D%5Cmathbb+E_%7B%28x%2Cy%29%2Cz_0%7D%5Cleft%5B-%5Clog+p_%5Cpsi%5Cbig%28y%5Cmid+x%2C+%5Chat+z_1%5Cbig%29%5Cright%5D%24%24++where+%24%5Chat+z_1%24+is+obtained+by+integrating+the+ODE+with+a+training-time+solver+%28can+be+few-step+Euler%29.++%23%23%23%23+%28iii%29+Contrastive+endpoint+anchoring+%28bridges+to+C2%29+Sample+wrong+answers+%24y%5E-%24+%28other+dataset+answers%2C+model+confusions%2C+or+arithmetic+near-misses%29.+Define+%24z%5E-%3D%5Cphi%28y%5E-%2Cc%29%24.+Add%3A++%24%24%5Cmathcal+L_%7B%5Ctext%7BNCE%7D%7D+%3D+-%5Clog+%5Cfrac%7B%5Cexp%28%5Cmathrm%7Bsim%7D%28%5Chat+z_1%2Cz%5E%5Cstar%29%2F%5Ctau%29%7D%7B%5Cexp%28%5Cmathrm%7Bsim%7D%28%5Chat+z_1%2Cz%5E%5Cstar%29%2F%5Ctau%29%2B%5Csum_%7Bk%7D%5Cexp%28%5Cmathrm%7Bsim%7D%28%5Chat+z_1%2Cz%5E-_k%29%2F%5Ctau%29%7D%24%24++%2A%2ATotal%3A%2A%2A++%24%24%5Cmathcal+L+%3D+%5Cmathcal+L_%7B%5Ctext%7BCFM%7D%7D+%2B+%5Clambda_%7B%5Ctext%7Bdec%7D%7D+%5Cmathcal+L_%7B%5Ctext%7Bdec%7D%7D+%2B+%5Clambda_%7B%5Ctext%7BNCE%7D%7D%5Cmathcal+L_%7B%5Ctext%7BNCE%7D%7D%24%24++%23%23%23+Rectified+reflow+%28few-step+distillation%29++Rectified+Flow+motivates+straightening+because+diffusion-style+generation+relies+on+numerical+solvers+and+can+be+costly.++The+rectified-flow+framework+constructs+a+rectified+flow+with+the+same+marginals+%28Theorem+3.3%29.+++%2A%2AAdaptation+to+conditional+reasoning%3A%2A%2A++%2A+Train+%24v_%5Ctheta%5E%7B%280%29%7D%24+with+%24%5Cmathcal+L%24.+%2A+For+reflow+iteration+%24k%3D1..K_%7B%5Ctext%7Breflow%7D%7D%24%3A++++1.+Sample+%24%28x%2Cy%29%24%2C+compute+%24c%24%2C+using+%24v_%5Ctheta%5E%7B%28k-1%29%7D%24+with+a+%2Ahigh-step%2A+solver+to+get+%24z_1%5E%7B%28k-1%29%7D%24.+++2.+%2A%2ADistill%2A%2A+a+neCFM+on+endpoints+%24%28z_0%2C+z_1%5E%7B%28k-1%29%7D%29%24%2C+%2A%2Abut+keep+%24%5Cmathcal+L_%7B%5Ctext%7Bdec%7D%7D%24%2A%2A+so+the+endpoint+still+decodes+to+%24y%24.++This+is+%E2%80%9Ctrajectory+straightening+by+self-distillation%2C%E2%80%9D+while+anchoring+correctness+through+decoding.++%23%23%23+Inference+procedure+%28compute+knobs+%2B+stopping%29++%2A%2AKnobs%3A%2A%2A++%2A+%24N%24+%3D+number+of+ODE+steps+%281%E2%80%9332%29+%2A+Solver%3A+Euler+%2F+Heun+%2A+Early+stop%3A+if+decoded+answer+is+stable+across+last+2+steps+OR+confidence+threshold+reached.++%2A%2APseudocode+%28inference%29%2A%2A++%60%60%60python+def+flow_of_thought_answer%28x%2C+N%2C+solver%3D%22euler%22%2C+conf_thresh%3D0.9%29%3A+++++c+%3D+Enc%28x%29+++++z+%3D+Normal%280%2C+I%29.sample%28%29+++++prev_ans+%3D+None+++++for+i+in+range%28N%29%3A+++++++++t+%3D+i+%2F+N+++++++++v+%3D+v_theta%28z%2C+t%2C+c%29+++++++++if+solver+%3D%3D+%22euler%22%3A+++++++++++++z+%3D+z+%2B+%281%2FN%29+%2A+v+++++++++elif+solver+%3D%3D+%22heun%22%3A+++++++++++++z_pred+%3D+z+%2B+%281%2FN%29+%2A+v+++++++++++++v_pred+%3D+v_theta%28z_pred%2C+%28i%2B1%29%2FN%2C+c%29+++++++++++++z+%3D+z+%2B+%281%2F%282%2AN%29%29+%2A+%28v+%2B+v_pred%29++++++++++ans%2C+conf+%3D+decode_answer%28p_psi%2C+x%2C+z%29++%23+answer-only+decoding+++++++++if+prev_ans+is+not+None+and+ans+%3D%3D+prev_ans+and+conf+%3E%3D+conf_thresh%3A+++++++++++++break+++++++++prev_ans+%3D+ans+++++return+ans+%60%60%60++%23%23+What+is+technically+new++%2A%2ANew+piece+%3D+%E2%80%9Canswer-endpoint+latent+flow+matching+for+reasoning%E2%80%9D+%2B+%E2%80%9Crectified+few-step+frontier.%E2%80%9D%2A%2A++%2A+%2A%2AObjective+novelty%3A%2A%2A+Apply+CFM-style+endpoint+regression+%28Flow+Matching%29+to+%2A%2Alatent+reasoning+states%2A%2A+whose+target+is+%2A%2Aanswer-conditioned%2A%2A+%24z%5E%5Cstar%3D%5Cphi%28y%2Cc%29%24%2C+rather+than+unconditional+generation+or+token+diffusion.+This+uses+the+%2Aform%2A+of+CFM+losses+%28Eq.+23-style+regression+along+an+interpolation%29+but+with+a+reasoning-specific+endpoint.++%2A+%2A%2AInference+novelty%3A%2A%2A+Use+%2A%2Arectified+reflow%2A%2A+to+make+a+%2Afew-step%2A+knob+meaningful+for+reasoning+correctness%2C+explicitly+motivated+by+solver+cost+in+diffusion%2FODE+sampling.++%2A+%2A%2ANovelty+vs+Coconut%3A%2A%2A+Coconut%E2%80%99s+latent+reasoning+is+trained+via+a+%2A%2Amulti-stage+strategy+guins%2A%2A%2C+and+removing+that+strategy+collapses+gains.+++++We+remove+the+need+for+intermediate+chains+by+learning+trajector+should+work+%28mechanistic+intuition%29+%2A+The+latent+ODE+is+a+%2A%2Alearned+iterative+refinement+process%2A%2A%3A+each+step+can+be+interpreted+as+updating+an+internal+%E2%80%9Cscratch+state%E2%80%9D+%28z%29+connmakes+the+target+%2Asemantically+aligned+with+the+correct+answer%2A%2C+while+the+decoder+loss+makes+the+endpoint+%2Aoperationally%2A+correct.+%2A+Rectification+distills+curved+trajectories+into+straighter+ones%2C+which+should+reduce+required+steps+%28analogous+to+distilling+many-step+generation+into+few-step+generation%29.++++%23%23%23+Dataset+%28contamination-resistant%29++%2A+%2A%2ASynthetic+multi-step+arithmetic+word+problems%2A%2A+generated+from+templates+%28e.ctor+sentences%29.+%2A+Ground+truth+computed+programmatically%3B+answers+canonicalized+%28string+normalized%29.+%2A+Hold+out%3A++++%2A+templates+%28OOD+wording%29%2C+++%2A+operation+depth+%28train+%E2%89%A44+ops%2C+test+5%E2%80%936+ops%29%2C+++%2A+number+ranges+%28train+2-digit%2C+test+3%E2%80%934+digit%29.++%23%23%23+Model+%28small+but+meaningful%29++%2A+%24d_z%3D256%24+latent.+%2A+Encoder%3A+small+Transformer+%28or+frozen+small+LM%29.+%2A+Vector+field+%24v_%5Ctheta%24%3A+6%E2%80%9312+layer+MLP%2FTransformer+over+%24%5Bz%2C+%5Ctext%7Btime-emb%7D%2C+c%5D%24.+%2A+Decoder%3A+answer-only+generator+%28often+%3C10+tokens%29.++%23%23%23+Baselines+%28minimum+set%29++1.+AR+model+trained+to+output+answer+directly+%28no+CoT%29%2C+matched+params.+2.+AR+%2B+self-consistency-style+sampling+%28but+answer-only+outputs%3B+compare+compute%29.+%28Self-consistency+is+sample-heavy+in+the+original+form.+%29+3.+A+masked+iterative+refinement+baseline+%28tiny+MDLM-style+unmasking+head%29+to+test+%E2%80%9Citerative+refinement+alone%E2%80%9D+vs+%E2%80%9Clatent+flow.%E2%80%9D++%23%23%23+Success+criterion++%2A+%2A%2AFrontier+win%3A%2A%2A+At+%24N%5Cin%5C%7B1%2C2%2C4%5C%7D%24+steps%2C+Flow-of-Thought+%E2%89%A5+AR+direct-answer+accuracy+at+matched+latency%2FFLOPs+%2A%2Aand%2A%2A+shows+monotonic+accuracy+improvement.+%2A+%2A%2ARobustness+improvement%3A%2A%2A+Smaller+relative+drop+on+held-out+templates%2Fformat+shifts+than+AR.++---++%23+Experimental+plan+++%23%23+Benchmarks+%2F+tasks+%28%E2%89%A52+standard+%2B+%E2%89%A51+stress+suite%29++%2A%2AStandard+tasks+%28reasoning%29%3A%2A%2A++1.+GSM8K+%28final+answer+only%3B+strip+rationales%29+2.+MATH+%28final+answer+only%3B+parseable+subset+first%29++%2A%2AStress+%2F+OOD+suite+%28tailored%29%3A%2A%2A++%2A+%2A%2AFormat+shift%3A%2A%2A+reorder+sentences%2C+change+units%2Fnumber+formatting%2C+add+irrelevant+distractor+facts.+%2A+%2A%2ATemplate+OOD%3A%2A%2A+paraphrase+problems+%28backtranslation+%2F+LLM+paraphrase%29+with+disjoint+templates.+%2A+%2A%2ALength%2Fgeneralization%3A%2A%2A+extrapolate+to+larger+numbers+%2F+deeper+compositional+depth+%28synthetic+%2B+MATH+subset%29.+%2A+%2A%2AReversal-like+tests%3A%2A%2A+%E2%80%9Cgiven+result%2C+infer+input%E2%80%9D+style+variants+for+synthetic+arithmetic+%28controlled+analog+of+reversal-curse+probes%3B+compare+to+diffusion+claims+like+LLaDA%29.+%28%5BarXiv%5D%5B2%5D%29++%23%23+Baselines+%28strong%2C+explicit+variants%29++%2A%2AAutoregressive+%28must+include%29%3A%2A%2A++%2A+AR+direct-answer+SFT+%28no+CoT%29.+%2A+AR+CoT+SFT+%2B+answer+extraction+%28upper+bound+but+emits+CoT%29.+%2A+CoT+prompting+%28few-shot%29+baseline.++%2A+Self-consistency+over+CoT+%28report+compute+carefully%3B+it+samples+many+outputs+in+the+paper%29.+++%2A%2ALatent%2Fiterative+refinement+%28must+include%29%3A%2A%2A++%2A+Coconut+%28if+reproducible+in+your+stack%29+and+its+no-curriculum+ablation+as+referenced+by+their+own+finding.++%2A+MDLM-style+masked+diffusion+fine-tuned+tokens+masked%2Funmasked%29.++%2A+Discrete+Flow+Matching+%28DFM%29+or+simil%28%5Bproceedings.neurips.cc%5D%5B1%5D%29+%2A+LLaDA-style+masked+diffusion+%28if+available+code%2Fmodel%29+as+a+high-capacity+diffusion+LM+baseline.+%28%5BarXiv%5D%5B2%5D%29+%2A+Flow+matching+for++few+steps+%28FlowSeq%29+as+a+%E2%80%9Cfew-step+FM+for+text%E2%80%9D+comparator.+%28%5Baclanthology.org%5D%5B4%5D%29+%2A+Latent+diffusi+%E2%80%9Cdiffusion-in-latent%E2%80%9D+comparator.+%28%5BarXiv%5D%5B3%5D%29++%2A%2ACompute+normalization+rule+%28pre-registered%29%3A%2A%2A++%2A+Primary+x-axis%3A+%2A%2A%23model+calls%2A%2A+%28vector-field+evals+%2F+denoiser+evals+%2F+forward+passes%29+and+wall-clock+on+fixed+hardware.+%2A+Secondary%3A+approximate+FLOPs.++%23%23+Metrics+%28primary+%2B+%E2%89%A53+secondary%29++%2A%2APrimary%3A%2A%2A+Exact-answer+accuracy+%28with+strict+parsing+rules%3B+ambiguous+answers+counted+wrong+unless+normalized%29.++%2A%2ASecondary+%28%E2%89%A53%29%3A%2A%2A++1.+%2A%2ACompute+frontier%3A%2A%2A+accuracy+vs+%28steps%2C+NFE%2C+wall-clock%2C+%24+cost%29.+2.+%2A%2ARobustness%3A%2A%2A+relative+accuracy+drop+under+each+stress+test%3B+report+worst-case+across+perturbations.+3.+%2A%2ACalibration%3A%2A%2A+ECE+on+answer+correctness+using+decoder+confidence+%28or+ensemble+variance%29.+4.+%2A%2AStability+%2F+variance%3A%2A%2A+min%2Fmedian%2Fmax+over+seeds%3B+tail+metrics+%285th+percentile+across+seeds%29.+5.+%28Optional%29+%2A%2AConsistency%3A%2A%2A+agreement+under+paraphrases+%28same+problem+paraphrased+K+ways%29.++%23%23+Stress+tests+%28systematic+%2B+worst-case%29++For+each+test+example%2C+generate+%24M%24+perturbations%3A++%2A+distractor+insertion+%280%2F1%2F3+facts%29%2C+%2A+unit+conversion+%2F+number+formatting%2C+%2A+sentence+order+shuffle%2C+%2A+paraphrase+style+changes.++Report%3A++%2A+mean+accuracy+across+perturbations%2C+%2A+%2A%2Aworst-case+accuracy%2A%2A+per+example+%28min+over+perturbations%29%2C+%2A+and+distribution+%28percentiles%29.++%23%23+Ablations+%26+sensitivity++%2A%2ACore+ablations%3A%2A%2A++%2A+Remove+rectification%2Freflow+%28train+once%3B+vary+solver+steps%29.+%2A+Endpoint+definition+variants%3A++++%2A+EOS+hidden+vs+pooled+answer-token+hidden%2C+++%2A+frozen+vs+learned+%24%5Cphi%24%2C+++%2A+with%2Fwithout+paraphrase-consistency+regularizer.+%2A+Remove+decoder+loss+%24%5Cmathcal+L_%7B%5Ctext%7Bdec%7D%7D%24+%28tests+whether+CFM+alone+is+sufficient%29.+%2A+Remove+contrastive+negatives+%28tests+collapse%2Fshortcut%29.+%2A+Path+family+variants%3A++++%2A+linear+path+%24z_t%3D%281-t%29z_0%2Bt+z%5E%5Cstar%24%2C+++%2A+learned+coupling+%2F+OT-inspired+path+%28if+you+implement%29.++%2A%2ASensitivity+sweeps%3A%2A%2A++++%2A+Steps+%24N%5Cin%5C%7B1%2C2%2C4%2C8%2C16%2C32%5C%7D%24+++%2A+Reflow+iterations+%24K_%7B%5Ctext%7Breflow%7D%7D%5Cin%5C%7B0%2C1%2C2%2C4%5C%7D%24+++%2A+Data+scaling+curves+%2810%25%2C+30%25%2C+100%25+of+training+set%29++%23%23+Statistical+rigor++%2A+%2A%2ASeeds%3A%2A%2A+%24%5Cgeq+5%24+seeds+for+small%2Fmedium+models%3B+%24%5Cgeq+3%24+for+large+%28pre-register%29.+%2A+%2A%2ACIs%3A%2A%2A+bootstrap+CI+for+accuracy%3B+paired+bootstrap+for+baseline+comparisons.+%2A+%2A%2ASignificance%3A%2A%2A+McNemar+test+%28paired+classification%29+where+applicable%3B+adjust+for+multiple+comparisons+on+stress+suites.++%2A%2APre-registered+key+comparisons+%28must+beat%29%3A%2A%2A++%2A+At+fixed+compute+budget+%28e.g.%2C+4+forward+calls%29%2C+Flow-of-Thought+must+beat%3A++++%2A+AR+direct-answer+SFT+++%2A+MDLM%2FDFM+few-step+variants+%2A+At+fixed+accuracy+%28e.g.%2C+60%25+on+GSM8K%29%2C+Flow-of-Thought+must+use+fewer+calls+than+AR%2BSC.++%23%23+Reliability+%26+leakage+controls+%28reasoning+benchmarks%29++%2A+%2A%2ANo-CoT+protocol%3A%2A%2A+training+data+contains+only+final+answers%3B+remove%2Fstrip+rationales.+%2A+%2A%2ASplit+hygiene%3A%2A%2A+verify+no+near-duplicate+overlap+between+train%2Ftest+%28minhash+%2F+n-gram+overlap%29.+%2A+%2A%2ATemplate+leakage%3A%2A%2A+for+synthetic+data%2C+split+by+%2Agenerator+template+id%2A%2C+not+random.+%2A+%2A%2APrompt+leakage%3A%2A%2A+randomize+prompt+wrappers+per+split%3B+evaluate+with+unseen+wrappers.+%2A+%2A%2AContamination+checks%3A%2A%2A+run+substring+search+of+test+problems+against+training+corpus+%28and+against+any+additional+scraped+data+you+use%29+to+detect+leakage%3B+report+flagged+rate+and+%E2%80%9Cclean+subset%E2%80%9D+results.++---+++%5B1%5D%3A+https%3A%2F%2Fproceedings.neurips.cc%2Fpaper_files%2Fpaper%2F2024%2Fhash%2Ff0d629a734b56a642701bba7bc8bb3ed-Abstract-Conference.html%3Futm_source%3Dchatgpt.com+%22Discrete+Flow+Matching%22+%5B2%5D%3A+https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fabs%2F2502.09992%3Futm_source%3Dchatgpt.com+%22Large+Language+Diffusion+Models%22+%5B3%5D%3A+https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fabs%2F2212.09462%3Futm_source%3Dchatgpt.com+%22Latent+Diffusion+for+Language+Generation%22+%5B4%5D%3A+https%3A%2F%2Faclanthology.org%2F2024.eacl-short.33%2F%3Futm_source%3Dchatgpt.com+%22Flow+Matching+for+Conditional+Text+Generation+in+a+Few+Sampling+Steps+-+ACL+Anthology%22&per_page=15&mailto=researchclaw%40users.noreply.github.com&select=id%2Ctitle%2Cauthorships%2Cpublication_year%2Cprimary_location%2Ccited_by_count%2Cdoi%2Cids%2Cabstract_inverted_index%2Ctype
S2 HTTP 414 for https://api.semanticscholar.org/graph/v1/paper/search?query=++%23+Flow+of+Thought++Given+supervised+pairs+%24%28x%2Cy%29%24+where+%24y%24+is+%2A%2Afinal+answer+only%2A%2A+%28no+chain-of-thought%29%2C+we+can+learn+a+%2A%2Aprompt-conditioned+latent+ODE%2A%2A+%24%5Cfrac%7Bdz%7D%7Bdt%7D%3Dv_%5Ctheta%28z%2Ct%2Cc%29%24+that+transports+a+simple+prior+%24z%280%29%5Csim%5Cmathcal+N%280%2CI%29%24+to+an+%2A%2Aanswer-conditioned+latent+endpoint%2A%2A+%24z%5E%5Cstar%3D%5Cphi%28y%2Cc%29%24%2C+such+that+decoding+from+%24z%281%29%24+yields+correct+answers+at+competitive+accuracy+%2A%2Awithout+emitting+CoT%2A%2A.++By+applying+%2A%2Arectified+flow+%2F+reflow%2A%2A+to+the+learned+latent+dynamics%2C+we+can+%E2%80%9Cstraighten%E2%80%9D+trajectories+so+that+%2A%2A1%E2%80%934+solver+steps%2A%2A+suffice+at+inference+time%2C+producing+a+tunable+%2A%2Acompute-quality+frontier%2A%2A+%28accuracy+vs.+steps%2Flatency%29+rather+than+a+fixed-cost+reasoning+procedure.+Rectified+flow+is+specifically+motivated+by+the+high+cost+of+ODE%2FSDE-based+sampling+in+diffusion-style+models.+++With+conditional+flow+matching+from+%24z_0%5Csim%5Cmathcal+N%280%2CI%29%24+to+%24z%5E%5Cstar%3D%5Cphi%28y%2Cc%29%24%2C+plus+%2A%2Arectified+reflow+distillation%2A%2A+to+enable+1%E2%80%934-step+inference.+Uses+CoT-free+supervision+%28answer+only%29.++---++%23%23+Method+specification++%23%23%23+Notation+%26+setup++%2A+Dataset+%24%5Cmathcal+D%3D%5C%7B%28x_i%2Cy_i%29%5C%7D%24+where+%24y%24+is+the+%2A%2Afinal+answer+string%2A%2A+%28no+rationales%29.+%2A+Prompt+encoder+%24c%3D%5Cmathrm%7BEnc%7D_%5Comega%28x%29%24+%28could+be+a+frozen+LM+trunk+or+trainable+encoder%29.+%2A+Answer-latent+encoder+%24z%5E%5Cstar%3D%5Cphi_%5Ceta%28y%2Cc%29%5Cin%5Cmathbb+R%5E%7Bd_z%7D%24.+%2A+Latent+dynamics%3A+%24%5Cfrac%7Bdz%7D%7Bdt%7D%3Dv_%5Ctheta%28z%2Ct%2Cc%29%24%2C+%24t%5Cin%5B0%2C1%5D%24%2C+%24z%280%29%3Dz_0%5Csim%5Cmathcal+N%280%2CI%29%24.+%2A+Decoder+%24p_%5Cpsi%28y%5Cmid+x%2C+z%281%29%29%24+that+emits+%2A%2Aanswer+only%2A%2A.++%23%23%23+Endpoint+construction+%24z%5E%5Cstar%3D%5Cphi_%5Ceta%28y%2Cc%29%24+%28crucial%29++You+want+an+endpoint+that%3A++1.+contains+answer+semantics%2C+2%29+is+stable+across+paraphrases%2C+3%29+doesn%E2%80%99t+leak+CoT.++Concrete+choice%3A++%2A+Use+a+frozen+pretrained+LM+%24%28F%29%24.+Run+%24%28F%29%24+on+the+concatenation+%24%5Bx+%5Cmid+%5Ctexttt%7B%3CANS%3E%7D+%5Cmid+y%5D%24.+%2A+Let+%24h_%7B%5Ctext%7Beos%7D%7D%24+be+the+final-layer+hidden+state+at+the+EOS+token+%28or+pooled+answer-token+hidden+states%29.+%2A+Set+%24z%5E%5Cstar+%3D+W+h_%7B%5Ctext%7Beos%7D%7D%24+with+a+learned+projection+%24W%5Cin%5Cmathbb+R%5E%7Bd_z%5Ctimes+d_h%7D%24.+++This+makes+%24z%5E%5Cstar%24+a+%2A%2Arepresentation+of+the+correct+answer+given+the+prompt%2A%2A%2C+without+needing+intermediate+rationales.++%23%23%23+Training+objectives++%23%23%23%23+%28i%29+Conditional+Flow+Matching+loss+%28endpoint-only+%E2%80%9Cteacher%E2%80%9D+path%29++Use+the+simplest+linear+coupling+path+%28mirrors+CFM-style+linear+interpolation+objectives%29.+In+Flow+Matching%2C+CFM+yields+objectives+of+the+form+in+Eq.+%2823%29+for+an+interpolation+%24%5Cpsi_t%24.+++For+our+latent+endpoints%3A++%2A+Sample+%24t%5Csim+%5Cmathcal+U%5B0%2C1%5D%24%2C+%24z_0%5Csim%5Cmathcal+N%280%2CI%29%24+%2A+Define+interpolation%3A+%24z_t%3D%281-t%29z_0%2Bt+z%5E%5Cstar%24+%2A+Target+velocity%3A+%24u+%3D+z%5E%5Cstar+-+z_0%24+%2A+Loss%3A++%24%24%5Cmathcal+L_%7B%5Ctext%7BCFM%7D%7D%28%5Ctheta%29%3D%5Cmathbb+E_%7B%28x%2Cy%29%2Cz_0%2Ct%7D%5Cleft%5B%7Cv_%5Ctheta%28z_t%2Ct%2Cc%29-u%7C_2%5E2%5Cright%5D%24%24++This+is+the+digressing+a+vector+field+along+an+interpolation+path%2C+consistent+with+Flow+Matching-style+regression+objectives.+++%23%23%23%23+%28ii%29+Answer+decoding+loss+%28forces+correctness%2C+discourages+degenerate+endpoints%29++%24%24%5Cmathcal+L_%7B%5Ctext%7Bdec%7D%7D%28%5Cpsi%29%3D%5Cmathbb+E_%7B%28x%2Cy%29%2Cz_0%7D%5Cleft%5B-%5Clog+p_%5Cpsi%5Cbig%28y%5Cmid+x%2C+%5Chat+z_1%5Cbig%29%5Cright%5D%24%24++where+%24%5Chat+z_1%24+is+obtained+by+integrating+the+ODE+with+a+training-time+solver+%28can+be+few-step+Euler%29.++%23%23%23%23+%28iii%29+Contrastive+endpoint+anchoring+%28bridges+to+C2%29+Sample+wrong+answers+%24y%5E-%24+%28other+dataset+answers%2C+model+confusions%2C+or+arithmetic+near-misses%29.+Define+%24z%5E-%3D%5Cphi%28y%5E-%2Cc%29%24.+Add%3A++%24%24%5Cmathcal+L_%7B%5Ctext%7BNCE%7D%7D+%3D+-%5Clog+%5Cfrac%7B%5Cexp%28%5Cmathrm%7Bsim%7D%28%5Chat+z_1%2Cz%5E%5Cstar%29%2F%5Ctau%29%7D%7B%5Cexp%28%5Cmathrm%7Bsim%7D%28%5Chat+z_1%2Cz%5E%5Cstar%29%2F%5Ctau%29%2B%5Csum_%7Bk%7D%5Cexp%28%5Cmathrm%7Bsim%7D%28%5Chat+z_1%2Cz%5E-_k%29%2F%5Ctau%29%7D%24%24++%2A%2ATotal%3A%2A%2A++%24%24%5Cmathcal+L+%3D+%5Cmathcal+L_%7B%5Ctext%7BCFM%7D%7D+%2B+%5Clambda_%7B%5Ctext%7Bdec%7D%7D+%5Cmathcal+L_%7B%5Ctext%7Bdec%7D%7D+%2B+%5Clambda_%7B%5Ctext%7BNCE%7D%7D%5Cmathcal+L_%7B%5Ctext%7BNCE%7D%7D%24%24++%23%23%23+Rectified+reflow+%28few-step+distillation%29++Rectified+Flow+motivates+straightening+because+diffusion-style+generation+relies+on+numerical+solvers+and+can+be+costly.++The+rectified-flow+framework+constructs+a+rectified+flow+with+the+same+marginals+%28Theorem+3.3%29.+++%2A%2AAdaptation+to+conditional+reasoning%3A%2A%2A++%2A+Train+%24v_%5Ctheta%5E%7B%280%29%7D%24+with+%24%5Cmathcal+L%24.+%2A+For+reflow+iteration+%24k%3D1..K_%7B%5Ctext%7Breflow%7D%7D%24%3A++++1.+Sample+%24%28x%2Cy%29%24%2C+compute+%24c%24%2C+using+%24v_%5Ctheta%5E%7B%28k-1%29%7D%24+with+a+%2Ahigh-step%2A+solver+to+get+%24z_1%5E%7B%28k-1%29%7D%24.+++2.+%2A%2ADistill%2A%2A+a+neCFM+on+endpoints+%24%28z_0%2C+z_1%5E%7B%28k-1%29%7D%29%24%2C+%2A%2Abut+keep+%24%5Cmathcal+L_%7B%5Ctext%7Bdec%7D%7D%24%2A%2A+so+the+endpoint+still+decodes+to+%24y%24.++This+is+%E2%80%9Ctrajectory+straightening+by+self-distillation%2C%E2%80%9D+while+anchoring+correctness+through+decoding.++%23%23%23+Inference+procedure+%28compute+knobs+%2B+stopping%29++%2A%2AKnobs%3A%2A%2A++%2A+%24N%24+%3D+number+of+ODE+steps+%281%E2%80%9332%29+%2A+Solver%3A+Euler+%2F+Heun+%2A+Early+stop%3A+if+decoded+answer+is+stable+across+last+2+steps+OR+confidence+threshold+reached.++%2A%2APseudocode+%28inference%29%2A%2A++%60%60%60python+def+flow_of_thought_answer%28x%2C+N%2C+solver%3D%22euler%22%2C+conf_thresh%3D0.9%29%3A+++++c+%3D+Enc%28x%29+++++z+%3D+Normal%280%2C+I%29.sample%28%29+++++prev_ans+%3D+None+++++for+i+in+range%28N%29%3A+++++++++t+%3D+i+%2F+N+++++++++v+%3D+v_theta%28z%2C+t%2C+c%29+++++++++if+solver+%3D%3D+%22euler%22%3A+++++++++++++z+%3D+z+%2B+%281%2FN%29+%2A+v+++++++++elif+solver+%3D%3D+%22heun%22%3A+++++++++++++z_pred+%3D+z+%2B+%281%2FN%29+%2A+v+++++++++++++v_pred+%3D+v_theta%28z_pred%2C+%28i%2B1%29%2FN%2C+c%29+++++++++++++z+%3D+z+%2B+%281%2F%282%2AN%29%29+%2A+%28v+%2B+v_pred%29++++++++++ans%2C+conf+%3D+decode_answer%28p_psi%2C+x%2C+z%29++%23+answer-only+decoding+++++++++if+prev_ans+is+not+None+and+ans+%3D%3D+prev_ans+and+conf+%3E%3D+conf_thresh%3A+++++++++++++break+++++++++prev_ans+%3D+ans+++++return+ans+%60%60%60++%23%23+What+is+technically+new++%2A%2ANew+piece+%3D+%E2%80%9Canswer-endpoint+latent+flow+matching+for+reasoning%E2%80%9D+%2B+%E2%80%9Crectified+few-step+frontier.%E2%80%9D%2A%2A++%2A+%2A%2AObjective+novelty%3A%2A%2A+Apply+CFM-style+endpoint+regression+%28Flow+Matching%29+to+%2A%2Alatent+reasoning+states%2A%2A+whose+target+is+%2A%2Aanswer-conditioned%2A%2A+%24z%5E%5Cstar%3D%5Cphi%28y%2Cc%29%24%2C+rather+than+unconditional+generation+or+token+diffusion.+This+uses+the+%2Aform%2A+of+CFM+losses+%28Eq.+23-style+regression+along+an+interpolation%29+but+with+a+reasoning-specific+endpoint.++%2A+%2A%2AInference+novelty%3A%2A%2A+Use+%2A%2Arectified+reflow%2A%2A+to+make+a+%2Afew-step%2A+knob+meaningful+for+reasoning+correctness%2C+explicitly+motivated+by+solver+cost+in+diffusion%2FODE+sampling.++%2A+%2A%2ANovelty+vs+Coconut%3A%2A%2A+Coconut%E2%80%99s+latent+reasoning+is+trained+via+a+%2A%2Amulti-stage+strategy+guins%2A%2A%2C+and+removing+that+strategy+collapses+gains.+++++We+remove+the+need+for+intermediate+chains+by+learning+trajector+should+work+%28mechanistic+intuition%29+%2A+The+latent+ODE+is+a+%2A%2Alearned+iterative+refinement+process%2A%2A%3A+each+step+can+be+interpreted+as+updating+an+internal+%E2%80%9Cscratch+state%E2%80%9D+%28z%29+connmakes+the+target+%2Asemantically+aligned+with+the+correct+answer%2A%2C+while+the+decoder+loss+makes+the+endpoint+%2Aoperationally%2A+correct.+%2A+Rectification+distills+curved+trajectories+into+straighter+ones%2C+which+should+reduce+required+steps+%28analogous+to+distilling+many-step+generation+into+few-step+generation%29.++++%23%23%23+Dataset+%28contamination-resistant%29++%2A+%2A%2ASynthetic+multi-step+arithmetic+word+problems%2A%2A+generated+from+templates+%28e.ctor+sentences%29.+%2A+Ground+truth+computed+programmatically%3B+answers+canonicalized+%28string+normalized%29.+%2A+Hold+out%3A++++%2A+templates+%28OOD+wording%29%2C+++%2A+operation+depth+%28train+%E2%89%A44+ops%2C+test+5%E2%80%936+ops%29%2C+++%2A+number+ranges+%28train+2-digit%2C+test+3%E2%80%934+digit%29.++%23%23%23+Model+%28small+but+meaningful%29++%2A+%24d_z%3D256%24+latent.+%2A+Encoder%3A+small+Transformer+%28or+frozen+small+LM%29.+%2A+Vector+field+%24v_%5Ctheta%24%3A+6%E2%80%9312+layer+MLP%2FTransformer+over+%24%5Bz%2C+%5Ctext%7Btime-emb%7D%2C+c%5D%24.+%2A+Decoder%3A+answer-only+generator+%28often+%3C10+tokens%29.++%23%23%23+Baselines+%28minimum+set%29++1.+AR+model+trained+to+output+answer+directly+%28no+CoT%29%2C+matched+params.+2.+AR+%2B+self-consistency-style+sampling+%28but+answer-only+outputs%3B+compare+compute%29.+%28Self-consistency+is+sample-heavy+in+the+original+form.+%29+3.+A+masked+iterative+refinement+baseline+%28tiny+MDLM-style+unmasking+head%29+to+test+%E2%80%9Citerative+refinement+alone%E2%80%9D+vs+%E2%80%9Clatent+flow.%E2%80%9D++%23%23%23+Success+criterion++%2A+%2A%2AFrontier+win%3A%2A%2A+At+%24N%5Cin%5C%7B1%2C2%2C4%5C%7D%24+steps%2C+Flow-of-Thought+%E2%89%A5+AR+direct-answer+accuracy+at+matched+latency%2FFLOPs+%2A%2Aand%2A%2A+shows+monotonic+accuracy+improvement.+%2A+%2A%2ARobustness+improvement%3A%2A%2A+Smaller+relative+drop+on+held-out+templates%2Fformat+shifts+than+AR.++---++%23+Experimental+plan+++%23%23+Benchmarks+%2F+tasks+%28%E2%89%A52+standard+%2B+%E2%89%A51+stress+suite%29++%2A%2AStandard+tasks+%28reasoning%29%3A%2A%2A++1.+GSM8K+%28final+answer+only%3B+strip+rationales%29+2.+MATH+%28final+answer+only%3B+parseable+subset+first%29++%2A%2AStress+%2F+OOD+suite+%28tailored%29%3A%2A%2A++%2A+%2A%2AFormat+shift%3A%2A%2A+reorder+sentences%2C+change+units%2Fnumber+formatting%2C+add+irrelevant+distractor+facts.+%2A+%2A%2ATemplate+OOD%3A%2A%2A+paraphrase+problems+%28backtranslation+%2F+LLM+paraphrase%29+with+disjoint+templates.+%2A+%2A%2ALength%2Fgeneralization%3A%2A%2A+extrapolate+to+larger+numbers+%2F+deeper+compositional+depth+%28synthetic+%2B+MATH+subset%29.+%2A+%2A%2AReversal-like+tests%3A%2A%2A+%E2%80%9Cgiven+result%2C+infer+input%E2%80%9D+style+variants+for+synthetic+arithmetic+%28controlled+analog+of+reversal-curse+probes%3B+compare+to+diffusion+claims+like+LLaDA%29.+%28%5BarXiv%5D%5B2%5D%29++%23%23+Baselines+%28strong%2C+explicit+variants%29++%2A%2AAutoregressive+%28must+include%29%3A%2A%2A++%2A+AR+direct-answer+SFT+%28no+CoT%29.+%2A+AR+CoT+SFT+%2B+answer+extraction+%28upper+bound+but+emits+CoT%29.+%2A+CoT+prompting+%28few-shot%29+baseline.++%2A+Self-consistency+over+CoT+%28report+compute+carefully%3B+it+samples+many+outputs+in+the+paper%29.+++%2A%2ALatent%2Fiterative+refinement+%28must+include%29%3A%2A%2A++%2A+Coconut+%28if+reproducible+in+your+stack%29+and+its+no-curriculum+ablation+as+referenced+by+their+own+finding.++%2A+MDLM-style+masked+diffusion+fine-tuned+tokens+masked%2Funmasked%29.++%2A+Discrete+Flow+Matching+%28DFM%29+or+simil%28%5Bproceedings.neurips.cc%5D%5B1%5D%29+%2A+LLaDA-style+masked+diffusion+%28if+available+code%2Fmodel%29+as+a+high-capacity+diffusion+LM+baseline.+%28%5BarXiv%5D%5B2%5D%29+%2A+Flow+matching+for++few+steps+%28FlowSeq%29+as+a+%E2%80%9Cfew-step+FM+for+text%E2%80%9D+comparator.+%28%5Baclanthology.org%5D%5B4%5D%29+%2A+Latent+diffusi+%E2%80%9Cdiffusion-in-latent%E2%80%9D+comparator.+%28%5BarXiv%5D%5B3%5D%29++%2A%2ACompute+normalization+rule+%28pre-registered%29%3A%2A%2A++%2A+Primary+x-axis%3A+%2A%2A%23model+calls%2A%2A+%28vector-field+evals+%2F+denoiser+evals+%2F+forward+passes%29+and+wall-clock+on+fixed+hardware.+%2A+Secondary%3A+approximate+FLOPs.++%23%23+Metrics+%28primary+%2B+%E2%89%A53+secondary%29++%2A%2APrimary%3A%2A%2A+Exact-answer+accuracy+%28with+strict+parsing+rules%3B+ambiguous+answers+counted+wrong+unless+normalized%29.++%2A%2ASecondary+%28%E2%89%A53%29%3A%2A%2A++1.+%2A%2ACompute+frontier%3A%2A%2A+accuracy+vs+%28steps%2C+NFE%2C+wall-clock%2C+%24+cost%29.+2.+%2A%2ARobustness%3A%2A%2A+relative+accuracy+drop+under+each+stress+test%3B+report+worst-case+across+perturbations.+3.+%2A%2ACalibration%3A%2A%2A+ECE+on+answer+correctness+using+decoder+confidence+%28or+ensemble+variance%29.+4.+%2A%2AStability+%2F+variance%3A%2A%2A+min%2Fmedian%2Fmax+over+seeds%3B+tail+metrics+%285th+percentile+across+seeds%29.+5.+%28Optional%29+%2A%2AConsistency%3A%2A%2A+agreement+under+paraphrases+%28same+problem+paraphrased+K+ways%29.++%23%23+Stress+tests+%28systematic+%2B+worst-case%29++For+each+test+example%2C+generate+%24M%24+perturbations%3A++%2A+distractor+insertion+%280%2F1%2F3+facts%29%2C+%2A+unit+conversion+%2F+number+formatting%2C+%2A+sentence+order+shuffle%2C+%2A+paraphrase+style+changes.++Report%3A++%2A+mean+accuracy+across+perturbations%2C+%2A+%2A%2Aworst-case+accuracy%2A%2A+per+example+%28min+over+perturbations%29%2C+%2A+and+distribution+%28percentiles%29.++%23%23+Ablations+%26+sensitivity++%2A%2ACore+ablations%3A%2A%2A++%2A+Remove+rectification%2Freflow+%28train+once%3B+vary+solver+steps%29.+%2A+Endpoint+definition+variants%3A++++%2A+EOS+hidden+vs+pooled+answer-token+hidden%2C+++%2A+frozen+vs+learned+%24%5Cphi%24%2C+++%2A+with%2Fwithout+paraphrase-consistency+regularizer.+%2A+Remove+decoder+loss+%24%5Cmathcal+L_%7B%5Ctext%7Bdec%7D%7D%24+%28tests+whether+CFM+alone+is+sufficient%29.+%2A+Remove+contrastive+negatives+%28tests+collapse%2Fshortcut%29.+%2A+Path+family+variants%3A++++%2A+linear+path+%24z_t%3D%281-t%29z_0%2Bt+z%5E%5Cstar%24%2C+++%2A+learned+coupling+%2F+OT-inspired+path+%28if+you+implement%29.++%2A%2ASensitivity+sweeps%3A%2A%2A++++%2A+Steps+%24N%5Cin%5C%7B1%2C2%2C4%2C8%2C16%2C32%5C%7D%24+++%2A+Reflow+iterations+%24K_%7B%5Ctext%7Breflow%7D%7D%5Cin%5C%7B0%2C1%2C2%2C4%5C%7D%24+++%2A+Data+scaling+curves+%2810%25%2C+30%25%2C+100%25+of+training+set%29++%23%23+Statistical+rigor++%2A+%2A%2ASeeds%3A%2A%2A+%24%5Cgeq+5%24+seeds+for+small%2Fmedium+models%3B+%24%5Cgeq+3%24+for+large+%28pre-register%29.+%2A+%2A%2ACIs%3A%2A%2A+bootstrap+CI+for+accuracy%3B+paired+bootstrap+for+baseline+comparisons.+%2A+%2A%2ASignificance%3A%2A%2A+McNemar+test+%28paired+classification%29+where+applicable%3B+adjust+for+multiple+comparisons+on+stress+suites.++%2A%2APre-registered+key+comparisons+%28must+beat%29%3A%2A%2A++%2A+At+fixed+compute+budget+%28e.g.%2C+4+forward+calls%29%2C+Flow-of-Thought+must+beat%3A++++%2A+AR+direct-answer+SFT+++%2A+MDLM%2FDFM+few-step+variants+%2A+At+fixed+accuracy+%28e.g.%2C+60%25+on+GSM8K%29%2C+Flow-of-Thought+must+use+fewer+calls+than+AR%2BSC.++%23%23+Reliability+%26+leakage+controls+%28reasoning+benchmarks%29++%2A+%2A%2ANo-CoT+protocol%3A%2A%2A+training+data+contains+only+final+answers%3B+remove%2Fstrip+rationales.+%2A+%2A%2ASplit+hygiene%3A%2A%2A+verify+no+near-duplicate+overlap+between+train%2Ftest+%28minhash+%2F+n-gram+overlap%29.+%2A+%2A%2ATemplate+leakage%3A%2A%2A+for+synthetic+data%2C+split+by+%2Agenerator+template+id%2A%2C+not+random.+%2A+%2A%2APrompt+leakage%3A%2A%2A+randomize+prompt+wrappers+per+split%3B+evaluate+with+unseen+wrappers.+%2A+%2A%2AContamination+checks%3A%2A%2A+run+substring+search+of+test+problems+against+training+corpus+%28and+against+any+additional+scraped+data+you+use%29+to+detect+leakage%3B+report+flagged+rate+and+%E2%80%9Cclean+subset%E2%80%9D+results.++---+++%5B1%5D%3A+https%3A%2F%2Fproceedings.neurips.cc%2Fpaper_files%2Fpaper%2F2024%2Fhash%2Ff0d629a734b56a642701bba7bc8bb3ed-Abstract-Conference.html%3Futm_source%3Dchatgpt.com+%22Discrete+Flow+Matching%22+%5B2%5D%3A+https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fabs%2F2502.09992%3Futm_source%3Dchatgpt.com+%22Large+Language+Diffusion+Models%22+%5B3%5D%3A+https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fabs%2F2212.09462%3Futm_source%3Dchatgpt.com+%22Latent+Diffusion+for+Language+Generation%22+%5B4%5D%3A+https%3A%2F%2Faclanthology.org%2F2024.eacl-short.33%2F%3Futm_source%3Dchatgpt.com+%22Flow+Matching+for+Conditional+Text+Generation+in+a+Few+Sampling+Steps+-+ACL+Anthology%22&limit=15&fields=paperId%2Ctitle%2Cabstract%2Cyear%2Cvenue%2CcitationCount%2Cauthors%2CexternalIds%2Curl
arXiv HTTP 414 for https://export.arxiv.org/api/query?search_query=all%3A++%23+Flow+of+Thought++Given+supervised+pairs+%24%28x%2Cy%29%24+where+%24y%24+is+%2A%2Afinal+answer+only%2A%2A+%28no+chain-of-thought%29%2C+we+can+learn+a+%2A%2Aprompt-conditioned+latent+ODE%2A%2A+%24%5Cfrac%7Bdz%7D%7Bdt%7D%3Dv_%5Ctheta%28z%2Ct%2Cc%29%24+that+transports+a+simple+prior+%24z%280%29%5Csim%5Cmathcal+N%280%2CI%29%24+to+an+%2A%2Aanswer-conditioned+latent+endpoint%2A%2A+%24z%5E%5Cstar%3D%5Cphi%28y%2Cc%29%24%2C+such+that+decoding+from+%24z%281%29%24+yields+correct+answers+at+competitive+accuracy+%2A%2Awithout+emitting+CoT%2A%2A.++By+applying+%2A%2Arectified+flow+%2F+reflow%2A%2A+to+the+learned+latent+dynamics%2C+we+can+%E2%80%9Cstraighten%E2%80%9D+trajectories+so+that+%2A%2A1%E2%80%934+solver+steps%2A%2A+suffice+at+inference+time%2C+producing+a+tunable+%2A%2Acompute-quality+frontier%2A%2A+%28accuracy+vs.+steps%2Flatency%29+rather+than+a+fixed-cost+reasoning+procedure.+Rectified+flow+is+specifically+motivated+by+the+high+cost+of+ODE%2FSDE-based+sampling+in+diffusion-style+models.+++With+conditional+flow+matching+from+%24z_0%5Csim%5Cmathcal+N%280%2CI%29%24+to+%24z%5E%5Cstar%3D%5Cphi%28y%2Cc%29%24%2C+plus+%2A%2Arectified+reflow+distillation%2A%2A+to+enable+1%E2%80%934-step+inference.+Uses+CoT-free+supervision+%28answer+only%29.++---++%23%23+Method+specification++%23%23%23+Notation+%26+setup++%2A+Dataset+%24%5Cmathcal+D%3D%5C%7B%28x_i%2Cy_i%29%5C%7D%24+where+%24y%24+is+the+%2A%2Afinal+answer+string%2A%2A+%28no+rationales%29.+%2A+Prompt+encoder+%24c%3D%5Cmathrm%7BEnc%7D_%5Comega%28x%29%24+%28could+be+a+frozen+LM+trunk+or+trainable+encoder%29.+%2A+Answer-latent+encoder+%24z%5E%5Cstar%3D%5Cphi_%5Ceta%28y%2Cc%29%5Cin%5Cmathbb+R%5E%7Bd_z%7D%24.+%2A+Latent+dynamics%3A+%24%5Cfrac%7Bdz%7D%7Bdt%7D%3Dv_%5Ctheta%28z%2Ct%2Cc%29%24%2C+%24t%5Cin%5B0%2C1%5D%24%2C+%24z%280%29%3Dz_0%5Csim%5Cmathcal+N%280%2CI%29%24.+%2A+Decoder+%24p_%5Cpsi%28y%5Cmid+x%2C+z%281%29%29%24+that+emits+%2A%2Aanswer+only%2A%2A.++%23%23%23+Endpoint+construction+%24z%5E%5Cstar%3D%5Cphi_%5Ceta%28y%2Cc%29%24+%28crucial%29++You+want+an+endpoint+that%3A++1.+contains+answer+semantics%2C+2%29+is+stable+across+paraphrases%2C+3%29+doesn%E2%80%99t+leak+CoT.++Concrete+choice%3A++%2A+Use+a+frozen+pretrained+LM+%24%28F%29%24.+Run+%24%28F%29%24+on+the+concatenation+%24%5Bx+%5Cmid+%5Ctexttt%7B%3CANS%3E%7D+%5Cmid+y%5D%24.+%2A+Let+%24h_%7B%5Ctext%7Beos%7D%7D%24+be+the+final-layer+hidden+state+at+the+EOS+token+%28or+pooled+answer-token+hidden+states%29.+%2A+Set+%24z%5E%5Cstar+%3D+W+h_%7B%5Ctext%7Beos%7D%7D%24+with+a+learned+projection+%24W%5Cin%5Cmathbb+R%5E%7Bd_z%5Ctimes+d_h%7D%24.+++This+makes+%24z%5E%5Cstar%24+a+%2A%2Arepresentation+of+the+correct+answer+given+the+prompt%2A%2A%2C+without+needing+intermediate+rationales.++%23%23%23+Training+objectives++%23%23%23%23+%28i%29+Conditional+Flow+Matching+loss+%28endpoint-only+%E2%80%9Cteacher%E2%80%9D+path%29++Use+the+simplest+linear+coupling+path+%28mirrors+CFM-style+linear+interpolation+objectives%29.+In+Flow+Matching%2C+CFM+yields+objectives+of+the+form+in+Eq.+%2823%29+for+an+interpolation+%24%5Cpsi_t%24.+++For+our+latent+endpoints%3A++%2A+Sample+%24t%5Csim+%5Cmathcal+U%5B0%2C1%5D%24%2C+%24z_0%5Csim%5Cmathcal+N%280%2CI%29%24+%2A+Define+interpolation%3A+%24z_t%3D%281-t%29z_0%2Bt+z%5E%5Cstar%24+%2A+Target+velocity%3A+%24u+%3D+z%5E%5Cstar+-+z_0%24+%2A+Loss%3A++%24%24%5Cmathcal+L_%7B%5Ctext%7BCFM%7D%7D%28%5Ctheta%29%3D%5Cmathbb+E_%7B%28x%2Cy%29%2Cz_0%2Ct%7D%5Cleft%5B%7Cv_%5Ctheta%28z_t%2Ct%2Cc%29-u%7C_2%5E2%5Cright%5D%24%24++This+is+the+digressing+a+vector+field+along+an+interpolation+path%2C+consistent+with+Flow+Matching-style+regression+objectives.+++%23%23%23%23+%28ii%29+Answer+decoding+loss+%28forces+correctness%2C+discourages+degenerate+endpoints%29++%24%24%5Cmathcal+L_%7B%5Ctext%7Bdec%7D%7D%28%5Cpsi%29%3D%5Cmathbb+E_%7B%28x%2Cy%29%2Cz_0%7D%5Cleft%5B-%5Clog+p_%5Cpsi%5Cbig%28y%5Cmid+x%2C+%5Chat+z_1%5Cbig%29%5Cright%5D%24%24++where+%24%5Chat+z_1%24+is+obtained+by+integrating+the+ODE+with+a+training-time+solver+%28can+be+few-step+Euler%29.++%23%23%23%23+%28iii%29+Contrastive+endpoint+anchoring+%28bridges+to+C2%29+Sample+wrong+answers+%24y%5E-%24+%28other+dataset+answers%2C+model+confusions%2C+or+arithmetic+near-misses%29.+Define+%24z%5E-%3D%5Cphi%28y%5E-%2Cc%29%24.+Add%3A++%24%24%5Cmathcal+L_%7B%5Ctext%7BNCE%7D%7D+%3D+-%5Clog+%5Cfrac%7B%5Cexp%28%5Cmathrm%7Bsim%7D%28%5Chat+z_1%2Cz%5E%5Cstar%29%2F%5Ctau%29%7D%7B%5Cexp%28%5Cmathrm%7Bsim%7D%28%5Chat+z_1%2Cz%5E%5Cstar%29%2F%5Ctau%29%2B%5Csum_%7Bk%7D%5Cexp%28%5Cmathrm%7Bsim%7D%28%5Chat+z_1%2Cz%5E-_k%29%2F%5Ctau%29%7D%24%24++%2A%2ATotal%3A%2A%2A++%24%24%5Cmathcal+L+%3D+%5Cmathcal+L_%7B%5Ctext%7BCFM%7D%7D+%2B+%5Clambda_%7B%5Ctext%7Bdec%7D%7D+%5Cmathcal+L_%7B%5Ctext%7Bdec%7D%7D+%2B+%5Clambda_%7B%5Ctext%7BNCE%7D%7D%5Cmathcal+L_%7B%5Ctext%7BNCE%7D%7D%24%24++%23%23%23+Rectified+reflow+%28few-step+distillation%29++Rectified+Flow+motivates+straightening+because+diffusion-style+generation+relies+on+numerical+solvers+and+can+be+costly.++The+rectified-flow+framework+constructs+a+rectified+flow+with+the+same+marginals+%28Theorem+3.3%29.+++%2A%2AAdaptation+to+conditional+reasoning%3A%2A%2A++%2A+Train+%24v_%5Ctheta%5E%7B%280%29%7D%24+with+%24%5Cmathcal+L%24.+%2A+For+reflow+iteration+%24k%3D1..K_%7B%5Ctext%7Breflow%7D%7D%24%3A++++1.+Sample+%24%28x%2Cy%29%24%2C+compute+%24c%24%2C+using+%24v_%5Ctheta%5E%7B%28k-1%29%7D%24+with+a+%2Ahigh-step%2A+solver+to+get+%24z_1%5E%7B%28k-1%29%7D%24.+++2.+%2A%2ADistill%2A%2A+a+neCFM+on+endpoints+%24%28z_0%2C+z_1%5E%7B%28k-1%29%7D%29%24%2C+%2A%2Abut+keep+%24%5Cmathcal+L_%7B%5Ctext%7Bdec%7D%7D%24%2A%2A+so+the+endpoint+still+decodes+to+%24y%24.++This+is+%E2%80%9Ctrajectory+straightening+by+self-distillation%2C%E2%80%9D+while+anchoring+correctness+through+decoding.++%23%23%23+Inference+procedure+%28compute+knobs+%2B+stopping%29++%2A%2AKnobs%3A%2A%2A++%2A+%24N%24+%3D+number+of+ODE+steps+%281%E2%80%9332%29+%2A+Solver%3A+Euler+%2F+Heun+%2A+Early+stop%3A+if+decoded+answer+is+stable+across+last+2+steps+OR+confidence+threshold+reached.++%2A%2APseudocode+%28inference%29%2A%2A++%60%60%60python+def+flow_of_thought_answer%28x%2C+N%2C+solver%3D%22euler%22%2C+conf_thresh%3D0.9%29%3A+++++c+%3D+Enc%28x%29+++++z+%3D+Normal%280%2C+I%29.sample%28%29+++++prev_ans+%3D+None+++++for+i+in+range%28N%29%3A+++++++++t+%3D+i+%2F+N+++++++++v+%3D+v_theta%28z%2C+t%2C+c%29+++++++++if+solver+%3D%3D+%22euler%22%3A+++++++++++++z+%3D+z+%2B+%281%2FN%29+%2A+v+++++++++elif+solver+%3D%3D+%22heun%22%3A+++++++++++++z_pred+%3D+z+%2B+%281%2FN%29+%2A+v+++++++++++++v_pred+%3D+v_theta%28z_pred%2C+%28i%2B1%29%2FN%2C+c%29+++++++++++++z+%3D+z+%2B+%281%2F%282%2AN%29%29+%2A+%28v+%2B+v_pred%29++++++++++ans%2C+conf+%3D+decode_answer%28p_psi%2C+x%2C+z%29++%23+answer-only+decoding+++++++++if+prev_ans+is+not+None+and+ans+%3D%3D+prev_ans+and+conf+%3E%3D+conf_thresh%3A+++++++++++++break+++++++++prev_ans+%3D+ans+++++return+ans+%60%60%60++%23%23+What+is+technically+new++%2A%2ANew+piece+%3D+%E2%80%9Canswer-endpoint+latent+flow+matching+for+reasoning%E2%80%9D+%2B+%E2%80%9Crectified+few-step+frontier.%E2%80%9D%2A%2A++%2A+%2A%2AObjective+novelty%3A%2A%2A+Apply+CFM-style+endpoint+regression+%28Flow+Matching%29+to+%2A%2Alatent+reasoning+states%2A%2A+whose+target+is+%2A%2Aanswer-conditioned%2A%2A+%24z%5E%5Cstar%3D%5Cphi%28y%2Cc%29%24%2C+rather+than+unconditional+generation+or+token+diffusion.+This+uses+the+%2Aform%2A+of+CFM+losses+%28Eq.+23-style+regression+along+an+interpolation%29+but+with+a+reasoning-specific+endpoint.++%2A+%2A%2AInference+novelty%3A%2A%2A+Use+%2A%2Arectified+reflow%2A%2A+to+make+a+%2Afew-step%2A+knob+meaningful+for+reasoning+correctness%2C+explicitly+motivated+by+solver+cost+in+diffusion%2FODE+sampling.++%2A+%2A%2ANovelty+vs+Coconut%3A%2A%2A+Coconut%E2%80%99s+latent+reasoning+is+trained+via+a+%2A%2Amulti-stage+strategy+guins%2A%2A%2C+and+removing+that+strategy+collapses+gains.+++++We+remove+the+need+for+intermediate+chains+by+learning+trajector+should+work+%28mechanistic+intuition%29+%2A+The+latent+ODE+is+a+%2A%2Alearned+iterative+refinement+process%2A%2A%3A+each+step+can+be+interpreted+as+updating+an+internal+%E2%80%9Cscratch+state%E2%80%9D+%28z%29+connmakes+the+target+%2Asemantically+aligned+with+the+correct+answer%2A%2C+while+the+decoder+loss+makes+the+endpoint+%2Aoperationally%2A+correct.+%2A+Rectification+distills+curved+trajectories+into+straighter+ones%2C+which+should+reduce+required+steps+%28analogous+to+distilling+many-step+generation+into+few-step+generation%29.++++%23%23%23+Dataset+%28contamination-resistant%29++%2A+%2A%2ASynthetic+multi-step+arithmetic+word+problems%2A%2A+generated+from+templates+%28e.ctor+sentences%29.+%2A+Ground+truth+computed+programmatically%3B+answers+canonicalized+%28string+normalized%29.+%2A+Hold+out%3A++++%2A+templates+%28OOD+wording%29%2C+++%2A+operation+depth+%28train+%E2%89%A44+ops%2C+test+5%E2%80%936+ops%29%2C+++%2A+number+ranges+%28train+2-digit%2C+test+3%E2%80%934+digit%29.++%23%23%23+Model+%28small+but+meaningful%29++%2A+%24d_z%3D256%24+latent.+%2A+Encoder%3A+small+Transformer+%28or+frozen+small+LM%29.+%2A+Vector+field+%24v_%5Ctheta%24%3A+6%E2%80%9312+layer+MLP%2FTransformer+over+%24%5Bz%2C+%5Ctext%7Btime-emb%7D%2C+c%5D%24.+%2A+Decoder%3A+answer-only+generator+%28often+%3C10+tokens%29.++%23%23%23+Baselines+%28minimum+set%29++1.+AR+model+trained+to+output+answer+directly+%28no+CoT%29%2C+matched+params.+2.+AR+%2B+self-consistency-style+sampling+%28but+answer-only+outputs%3B+compare+compute%29.+%28Self-consistency+is+sample-heavy+in+the+original+form.+%29+3.+A+masked+iterative+refinement+baseline+%28tiny+MDLM-style+unmasking+head%29+to+test+%E2%80%9Citerative+refinement+alone%E2%80%9D+vs+%E2%80%9Clatent+flow.%E2%80%9D++%23%23%23+Success+criterion++%2A+%2A%2AFrontier+win%3A%2A%2A+At+%24N%5Cin%5C%7B1%2C2%2C4%5C%7D%24+steps%2C+Flow-of-Thought+%E2%89%A5+AR+direct-answer+accuracy+at+matched+latency%2FFLOPs+%2A%2Aand%2A%2A+shows+monotonic+accuracy+improvement.+%2A+%2A%2ARobustness+improvement%3A%2A%2A+Smaller+relative+drop+on+held-out+templates%2Fformat+shifts+than+AR.++---++%23+Experimental+plan+++%23%23+Benchmarks+%2F+tasks+%28%E2%89%A52+standard+%2B+%E2%89%A51+stress+suite%29++%2A%2AStandard+tasks+%28reasoning%29%3A%2A%2A++1.+GSM8K+%28final+answer+only%3B+strip+rationales%29+2.+MATH+%28final+answer+only%3B+parseable+subset+first%29++%2A%2AStress+%2F+OOD+suite+%28tailored%29%3A%2A%2A++%2A+%2A%2AFormat+shift%3A%2A%2A+reorder+sentences%2C+change+units%2Fnumber+formatting%2C+add+irrelevant+distractor+facts.+%2A+%2A%2ATemplate+OOD%3A%2A%2A+paraphrase+problems+%28backtranslation+%2F+LLM+paraphrase%29+with+disjoint+templates.+%2A+%2A%2ALength%2Fgeneralization%3A%2A%2A+extrapolate+to+larger+numbers+%2F+deeper+compositional+depth+%28synthetic+%2B+MATH+subset%29.+%2A+%2A%2AReversal-like+tests%3A%2A%2A+%E2%80%9Cgiven+result%2C+infer+input%E2%80%9D+style+variants+for+synthetic+arithmetic+%28controlled+analog+of+reversal-curse+probes%3B+compare+to+diffusion+claims+like+LLaDA%29.+%28%5BarXiv%5D%5B2%5D%29++%23%23+Baselines+%28strong%2C+explicit+variants%29++%2A%2AAutoregressive+%28must+include%29%3A%2A%2A++%2A+AR+direct-answer+SFT+%28no+CoT%29.+%2A+AR+CoT+SFT+%2B+answer+extraction+%28upper+bound+but+emits+CoT%29.+%2A+CoT+prompting+%28few-shot%29+baseline.++%2A+Self-consistency+over+CoT+%28report+compute+carefully%3B+it+samples+many+outputs+in+the+paper%29.+++%2A%2ALatent%2Fiterative+refinement+%28must+include%29%3A%2A%2A++%2A+Coconut+%28if+reproducible+in+your+stack%29+and+its+no-curriculum+ablation+as+referenced+by+their+own+finding.++%2A+MDLM-style+masked+diffusion+fine-tuned+tokens+masked%2Funmasked%29.++%2A+Discrete+Flow+Matching+%28DFM%29+or+simil%28%5Bproceedings.neurips.cc%5D%5B1%5D%29+%2A+LLaDA-style+masked+diffusion+%28if+available+code%2Fmodel%29+as+a+high-capacity+diffusion+LM+baseline.+%28%5BarXiv%5D%5B2%5D%29+%2A+Flow+matching+for++few+steps+%28FlowSeq%29+as+a+%E2%80%9Cfew-step+FM+for+text%E2%80%9D+comparator.+%28%5Baclanthology.org%5D%5B4%5D%29+%2A+Latent+diffusi+%E2%80%9Cdiffusion-in-latent%E2%80%9D+comparator.+%28%5BarXiv%5D%5B3%5D%29++%2A%2ACompute+normalization+rule+%28pre-registered%29%3A%2A%2A++%2A+Primary+x-axis%3A+%2A%2A%23model+calls%2A%2A+%28vector-field+evals+%2F+denoiser+evals+%2F+forward+passes%29+and+wall-clock+on+fixed+hardware.+%2A+Secondary%3A+approximate+FLOPs.++%23%23+Metrics+%28primary+%2B+%E2%89%A53+secondary%29++%2A%2APrimary%3A%2A%2A+Exact-answer+accuracy+%28with+strict+parsing+rules%3B+ambiguous+answers+counted+wrong+unless+normalized%29.++%2A%2ASecondary+%28%E2%89%A53%29%3A%2A%2A++1.+%2A%2ACompute+frontier%3A%2A%2A+accuracy+vs+%28steps%2C+NFE%2C+wall-clock%2C+%24+cost%29.+2.+%2A%2ARobustness%3A%2A%2A+relative+accuracy+drop+under+each+stress+test%3B+report+worst-case+across+perturbations.+3.+%2A%2ACalibration%3A%2A%2A+ECE+on+answer+correctness+using+decoder+confidence+%28or+ensemble+variance%29.+4.+%2A%2AStability+%2F+variance%3A%2A%2A+min%2Fmedian%2Fmax+over+seeds%3B+tail+metrics+%285th+percentile+across+seeds%29.+5.+%28Optional%29+%2A%2AConsistency%3A%2A%2A+agreement+under+paraphrases+%28same+problem+paraphrased+K+ways%29.++%23%23+Stress+tests+%28systematic+%2B+worst-case%29++For+each+test+example%2C+generate+%24M%24+perturbations%3A++%2A+distractor+insertion+%280%2F1%2F3+facts%29%2C+%2A+unit+conversion+%2F+number+formatting%2C+%2A+sentence+order+shuffle%2C+%2A+paraphrase+style+changes.++Report%3A++%2A+mean+accuracy+across+perturbations%2C+%2A+%2A%2Aworst-case+accuracy%2A%2A+per+example+%28min+over+perturbations%29%2C+%2A+and+distribution+%28percentiles%29.++%23%23+Ablations+%26+sensitivity++%2A%2ACore+ablations%3A%2A%2A++%2A+Remove+rectification%2Freflow+%28train+once%3B+vary+solver+steps%29.+%2A+Endpoint+definition+variants%3A++++%2A+EOS+hidden+vs+pooled+answer-token+hidden%2C+++%2A+frozen+vs+learned+%24%5Cphi%24%2C+++%2A+with%2Fwithout+paraphrase-consistency+regularizer.+%2A+Remove+decoder+loss+%24%5Cmathcal+L_%7B%5Ctext%7Bdec%7D%7D%24+%28tests+whether+CFM+alone+is+sufficient%29.+%2A+Remo